40:40.366 --> 40:41.433 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
observe nature?

40:41.433 --> 40:43.933 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
STUDENT: Like, with our nose?

40:43.933 --> 40:46.433 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
ARACELY MONTERO: With our noses.

40:46.433 --> 40:51.300 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
KAVITHA CARDOZA: Ranger
