the largest percentage
of park visitors overall.

44:33.033 --> 44:36.666 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JONATHAN JARVIS, Director,
National Park Service:
What we're feeling now
is that there's a new

44:36.666 --> 44:40.833 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
generation that is more
urban, more diverse.

44:40.833 --> 44:45.833 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
