country's evolving story.

45:06.066 --> 45:09.233 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JONATHAN JARVIS: Filling in
the gaps, as I would say,
in the American narrative.

45:09.233 --> 45:12.266 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
